.TH man 1 "07 April 2020" "0.1" "simple_shell man page"

.SH NAME
.B simple_shell - Command interpreter that reads from Standard Input.

.SH SYNOPSIS
./hsh [options] [file]

.SH DESCRIPTION
Simple_Shell is an command language interpreter which is compatible with sh. It will execute the commands read from the standard input.

.SH RETURN VALUE

If it is successful, it will return 0, otherwise if it fails, it will return other number.

.SH PATH

All the directions will be searched in the PATH env variable.

.SH OPTIONS
.B simple_shell
The command options will be entered after the main command, which will be followed by an space and the '-' character. 

.SH EXAMPLE

[command] [options]
$ ls -l

.SH SEE ALSO
.I "holberton.h"

.SH BUGS
Not known bugs, if you find one please report to 1561@holbertonschool.com or 1235@holbertonschool.com.
